data.description: This estate is located in the desirable gated community of Malibu Bay. The home consist of four bedrooms, three bathrooms, split floor plan which offers plenty of privacy, two car garage, volume ceilings, fenced, and with plenty of room for a swimming pool. The community amenities included a resort style swimming pool, fitness center, social room with kitchen, and Childers's play area.
